<div id="sdfootnote1">
	<p lang="en-GB" class="sdfootnote-western"><a class="sdfootnotesym-western" name="sdfootnote1sym" href="#sdfootnote1anc">1</a><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
	 See A/HRC/5/21, chap. III, paras. 60-62. </font>
	</p>
</div>
<div id="sdfootnote2">
	<p lang="en-GB" class="sdfootnote-western"><a class="sdfootnotesym-western" name="sdfootnote2sym" href="#sdfootnote2anc">a</a>
	 <font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">The universal periodic
	review is an evolving process; the Council, after the conclusion of
	the first review cycle, may review the modalities and the
	periodicity of this mechanism, based on best practices and lessons
	learned.</font></p>
</div>
<div id="sdfootnote3">
	<p lang="en-GB" class="sdfootnote-western"><a class="sdfootnotesym-western" name="sdfootnote3sym" href="#sdfootnote3anc">b</a>
	 <font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="en-US">A
	Universal Periodic Review Voluntary Trust Fund should be established
	to facilitate the participation of developing countries,
	particularly the Least Developed Countries, in the universal
	periodic review mechanism.</span></font></p>
</div>
<div id="sdfootnote4">
	<p lang="en-GB" class="sdfootnote-western"><a class="sdfootnotesym-western" name="sdfootnote4sym" href="#sdfootnote4anc">c</a>
	 <font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="en-US">A
	decision should be taken by the Council on whether to resort to
	existing financing mechanisms or to create a new mechanism.</span></font></p>
</div>
<div id="sdfootnote5">
	<p lang="en-GB" class="western" style="margin-bottom: 0.08in; line-height: 100%">
	<a class="sdfootnotesym-western" name="sdfootnote5sym" href="#sdfootnote5anc">d</a><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
	 </font><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="en-US">Country
	mandates meet the following criteria:</span></font></p>
	<ul>
		<li/>
<p class="western" style="margin-bottom: 0.08in; line-height: 100%">
		<font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">There is a pending mandate
		of the Council to be accomplished; or </font>
		</p>
		<li/>
<p class="western" style="margin-bottom: 0.08in; line-height: 100%">
		<font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">There is a pending mandate
		of the General Assembly to be accomplished; or</font></p>
		<li/>
<p lang="en-GB" class="western" style="margin-bottom: 0.17in; line-height: 100%">
		<font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="en-US">The
		nature of the mandate is for advisory services and technical
		assistance</span></font><font face="Arial Narrow, sans-serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="en-US">.</span></font></font></p>
	</ul>
</div>
<div id="sdfootnote6">
	<p lang="en-GB" class="sdfootnote-western"><a class="sdfootnotesym-western" name="sdfootnote6sym" href="#sdfootnote6anc">e</a><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
	 Figures indicated in square brackets refer to identical or
	corresponding rules of the General&nbsp;Assembly or its Main
	Committees (A/520/Rev.16).</font></p>
</div>
